By":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:05:01.000Z","msg":"淨軍事實力唔洗講大家都知邊知贏<br />\n但實際上，打熱戰之前，中美之間既博弈仲有好多未知數，11月大選如果trumptrump輸左，盤棋會逆轉。不過當然照現時局勢發展trump係冇乜可能輸，我都唔呢佢輸"},{"pid":"2a843be984d33d0fa8dcb281fb6539fe9651e62a","tid":2130604,"uid":21329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a1f8efff04668e2eae4e304e8bf0a5b4ec9a47","tid":2130604,"uid":21329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"574133990cfb3f9890a5d00e77fc4eb42d40825b","tid":2130604,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"越戰<br />\n韓戰<br />\n安哥拉內戰<br />\n盧旺達屠殺<br />\n蘇聯衛國戰爭<br />\n國共內戰"},{"pid":"2ad2194b19db406cbfc23dac07e91de025372bdd","tid":2130604,"uid":21329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:15:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"639998a8727c5dcf4aaa00ee1622653a4c9b34cd","tid":2130604,"uid":112583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4cdc5763a4aa0c87b9acb47a253f1d596e447301","tid":2130604,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n美國一打<br />\n荷里活明星、nba球星、tiktok網紅、左膠就會發動大規模反戰示威<br />\n美國最大敵人從來都係自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:17:02.000Z","msg":"美軍玩就玩斬首行動+精準打擊<br />\n好似上次個伊朗將軍咁， 上落車死左都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"340e7be95e9fef6988a5f624276604f98103a0cf","tid":2130604,"uid":21329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"大家覺得真係開打既機率大唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b707b1bf5eee995453c260b501dddd188d02f2","tid":2130604,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"我國必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2898de758c